function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	local champspawner = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorKilled, "deathSpawner")[1]

	Hydra.Wait(1.5)

		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(champspawner)
	end
	CHAMPS_SPAWNED = CHAMPS_SPAWNED + 1
	if CHAMPS_SPAWNED >= 2 then
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(addspawner)
	end
end
